support

Class Tag

  • java.lang.Object
    • support.Tag

  • public class Tag
extends java.lang.Object
    Tag class, append this to data that is written to CDB so we know where it came from.
    (k,j,i) = reservation k station line j thread i
    k = 0 = ADD/SUB k = 1 = MULT/DIV k = 2 = LOAD k = 3 = STORE
    Author:
    David
